node.text:
A brief guide to doing the Inktober challenge.⁣
Special thanks to @artsnacks for making the #inktober2020 art box. I seriously love these art boxes!⁣ ⁣
⁣
To order one hit the link in the @inktober profile.⁣
⁣
-Jake

node.text:
I’ll be a part of @lightboxexpo this year! ⁣
Tickets are on sale now for a 3 day online art event with all the top artists in entertainment, animation, video games and more. ⁣
⁣
Stay tuned for more info on what I’ll be presenting and sharing. In the meantime snag your tickets today.⁣
⁣
#lightbox #lightbox2021 #lbx2021 #lbxo2021 #lbxonline2021 #drawings #convention #artists #sketchbook #sketching #conceptart #scifiart #fantasyart #onlineconvention #lightboxexpo

STAR PRINCESS AVEN⁣

node.text:
SKULL CHASER vs THE MOUTH of GRAAG!⁣
⁣
Been having fun with Skull lately. Thinking of stories and situations. I drew the blast from the gun and didn’t like how it turned out so you can see the correction tape mess where I covered it up.⁣
⁣
#skullchaser #spacepunks #peril #danger #comicart #copicmarkers #copicgasenfude #comiccharacter #mondays⁣

node.text:
TWEETBOT.⁣
⁣
I did this for @tycarterart’s new “Artist in Residence” project he’s doing for Patreon. Each month Ty interviews an artist then the do a demo in real time and walk you through their process. You can watch me make this drawing from start to finish. It took me about 30 minutes and I tell all my tricks.⁣
⁣
I also walk you through my Snakemech drawing I did a few weeks ago. Good stuff, check it out!⁣
⁣
Go to @tycarterart and support his Patreon, link in his bio and my story.⁣
⁣
#tweetbot #twitterbot #birdrobo #twitter #comicart #comicartist #digitalart #robotart #mech #mecha #conceptsketch #conceptart

node.text:
SKULL vs MAIMOTH⁣
⁣
I was going to draw a Dinosaur monster and my kid (Calvin the Art Director) said I draw too many dinosaurs and to make it a mammoth monster. The kid is always right.⁣
⁣
Skull’s running pose was inspired by @philbourassa’s Impulse character sheet. I’m constantly in awe of Phil’s incredible poses he draws. ⁣
⁣
#skullchaser #spacepunks #comiccharacter #comicart #comicartist #illosketchbook #copicsketch #copicmarkers #mammoth #monster #monsterdesign

ABOMINABLE CHARLES CHRISTOPHER!⁣
⁣
Been a fan of @karlkerschl’s comic for ages, so I had to do some fan art.⁣
⁣
Karl’s running a Kickstarter:  @karlkerschl and you can actually get this drawing as a print in one of the tiers. Pretty cool.⁣
⁣
YouTube of this drawing coming this week.⁣
⁣

INSERT COIN FOR T-SHIRT⁣
⁣

⁣
Wearing this shirt might not make you an inter-galactic bounty hunter, but you'll feel cool that's for sure...and at the end of the day what more could you want?⁣
